Refactored theme architecture from SASS-based styling to consolidated Tailwind CSS files with inline Bootstrap-compatible components for three theme variants: Nord, InvoicePlane (default), and InvoicePlane Blue.

## Changes

- **Theme structure**: Created self-contained theme directories with consolidated `style-tailwind.css` files
  - `resources/assets/nord/css/` - Nord theme with Nord color palette via Tailwind v4 `@theme` tokens (Polar Night, Snow Storm, Frost, Aurora)
  - `resources/assets/invoiceplane/css/` - Default InvoicePlane theme with standard Bootstrap colors
  - `resources/assets/invoiceplane_blue/css/` - Blue variant of InvoicePlane theme
  - Each contains single consolidated `style-tailwind.css` file with all components inline

- **Build configuration**: Updated `vite.config.js` with entries for all three themes
  - `nord/css/style-tailwind` → outputs to `public/assets/nord/css/style-tailwind.css`
  - `invoiceplane/css/style-tailwind` → outputs to `public/assets/invoiceplane/css/style-tailwind.css`
  - `invoiceplane_blue/css/style-tailwind` → outputs to `public/assets/invoiceplane_blue/css/style-tailwind.css`
  - Maintains separate build artifacts for each theme

- **Bootstrap compatibility**: All themes include complete Bootstrap-compatible component styles inline
  - CSS custom properties for color variables extracted from SASS `_variables.scss`
  - All Bootstrap components inline: buttons (all variants and sizes), forms, tables, alerts, panels, pagination, utilities
  - InvoicePlane custom styles: headerbar, item tables, navigation, text ellipsis helpers, QR code tables, stamps
  - Single consolidated file per theme eliminates need for separate bootstrap-tailwind.css
  - Restored original `bootstrap-tailwind.css` (with standard Bootstrap colors) to `resources/assets/core/css/` for the core theme

## Theme Architecture

### Nord Theme (1008 lines)
```css
/* Nord color tokens in theme variant */
@theme {
    --color-polarnight-800: #2e3440;  /* Dark backgrounds */
    --color-frost-500: #88c0d0;       /* Primary accent */
